{"tid":1094500,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞透視[粵/普]","createTime":"2019-04-06T10:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T11:37:45.000Z","uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3267a4f1cfa87001015054dd99d542f88224389","tid":1094500,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"7:00PM<br />\n新聞透視[粵/普]      <br />\n<br />\n俗稱「共享單車」的無樁式自助單車租賃服務，已引入香港兩年，一間公司去年中已結業，一間公司應用程式已下架，另一間近日亦傳出財困。這種營運模式在港是否合適？留下的單車，處理責任誰屬？共享單車在其他地方成功以方便的租賃形式，增加市民以單車代步的意慾，但港府政策方針一直不鼓勵在市區踏單車，令共享單車無法全面成為「駁腳」工具。市區的道路有否空間容納更多單車？政府應如何配合？"},{"pid":"3e674b0be1113859a9474b993b997195b318498e","tid":1094500,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4300949dcae780087bef94a24d85def83f1e65b8","tid":1094500,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:05:23.000Z","msg":"少d好 次次對頭都驚炒埋黎我貴車"},{"pid":"feb7305b676b546c4863aab48f87e54f1248e333","tid":1094500,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"d85dde79668f825aa01342a19569c97fcb176f98","tid":1094500,"uid":188282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:11:28.000Z","msg":"有冇講共享單車真正目的係cap水?"},{"pid":"b4a84e9057b6cdedd598a87623d97568799aaa26","tid":1094500,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"d85dde79668f825aa01342a19569c97fcb176f98","tid":1094500,"uid":188282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:11:28.000Z","msg":"有冇講共享單車真正目的係cap水?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:12:33.000Z","msg":"未"},{"pid":"8691640ddb4cdc9f99e2defa17c890f85e9d6569","tid":1094500,"uid":8829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"要開account 要入錢真係有啲麻煩<br />\n寧願好似外國咁 可以每次俾錢<br />\n執笠都唔洗煩退錢"},{"pid":"6099b95fd72dfae8c61d1cf23a43c2e298d52eff","tid":1094500,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"